  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 13th level, You can weave a veil of psychic static to mask yourself. As an action, you can magically become <strong>invisible</strong>, along with anything you are wearing or carrying, for 1 hour or until you dismiss this effect (no action required). This invisibility ends early immediately after you deal damage to a creature or you force a creature to make a saving throw.</p><p>Once you use this feature, you can't do so again until you finish a <strong>long rest</strong>, unless you expend a @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.mVKtOzsuLaKbRJts]{Psionic Energy Die} to use this feature again.</p><section class=\"secret\" id=\"secret-i8QeBA4qVm6rBOwZ\"><p><em>Note: After adding this feature to your character, set Resource Consumption to Item Uses: Psionic Energy.</em></p></section>",
